{"tid":2291112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「45億年隕石」從天而降砸破屋頂 製棺師喜獲5千萬立刻退休","createTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T17:45:56.000Z","uid":56533,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9743670090ad9761c1c9df6123a74116e3923efd","tid":2291112,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/Oz4mQkTLRTdbCQMz6IlsQ1Mm-h0=/760x1023/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DE3AN5L2XVBUJJYFLBRIRETO6E.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOz4mQkTLRTdbCQMz6IlsQ1Mm-h0%3D%2F760x1023%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDE3AN5L2XVBUJJYFLBRIRETO6E.JPG&h=032143b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡塔嘉隆與美國太空隕石專家柯林斯(右)。<br />\n<br />\n這真是富貴逼人來！印尼一名製棺師傅的住處，日前突然有一塊橄欖球大小的石頭從天而降，把屋頂砸出一個洞，交由專家鑑定竟發現是一塊擁有45億年歷史的太空隕石，甚至可能含有足以解釋生命起源的成分！他將這塊天上掉下來的石頭以140萬英鎊(約台幣5297萬元)的代價賣給一位收藏家，並決定退休享受人生。<br />\n<br />\n《太陽報》報導，印尼北蘇門答臘33歲男子胡塔嘉隆(Josua Hutagalung)，是個製棺師傅，今年八月某日他人家門口製作一副棺材，突然「碰」的一聲，一塊橄欖球大小的石頭從天而降，把他家院子上方的屋頂砸出了一個洞。<br />\n<br />\n「我那時聽到一聲巨響，感覺房屋都在搖晃，感覺好像是一棵大樹砸到我們屋頂」，胡塔嘉隆憶述，隨即在院子土地上發現了一塊石頭，「當時石頭好燙，我們根本不能碰，之後我太太拿了鋤頭把石頭挖進屋內」。想不到這塊2.2公斤的石頭，成了他未來30年的薪水。<br />\n<br />\n胡塔嘉隆將這個天上掉下來的不速之客拍了照放上網，想知道到底是什麼，很快的，美國太空岩石專家柯林斯(Jared Collins)與他聯絡，並在最短時間趕到他家，「為了保護這塊隕石的安全」，柯林斯說：「我的手機上擠滿了各種瘋狂的報價，促使我立刻搭上飛機去買這塊隕石」，「當時還在新冠肺炎(武漢肺炎)嚴峻時期，老實說，我也還沒決定是該自己買下來，還是與美國的科學家收藏家一起合作」，「我只能帶著能湊到的所有現金去找胡塔嘉隆，沒想到他是個高超的談判者」。<br />\n<br />\n這塊隕石的一小塊重約1.839公克的碎片，後來被另一位收藏家以每公克757英鎊(約台幣2.86萬元)的價格買去，依此推估，總重達2.2公斤的這塊主石，價格至少超過140萬英鎊。<br />\n<br />\n柯林斯最後把這塊隕石帶到美國，由一位美籍收藏家買下，並送到亞利桑那大學隕石研究中心(the Centre for Meteorite Studies at Arizona State University)，存放在液態氮中。初步研究發現，這是一塊極為罕見的「CM 1/2 碳質球粒隕石」(CM1/2 carbonaceous Chondrite)，科學家相信，這類隕石中含有獨特的氨基酸，以及其他可激發生命起源的物質，至少來自45億年前。<br />\n<br />\n而幸運的胡塔嘉隆已經決定提前享受退休生活，育有3子的他說：「我一直想要個女兒，相信這是個好預兆，應該可以如願了」，他還打算為居住的社區興建一座教堂。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201118/LUAP3SKPE5D6HKBGAPT6CRVE7I/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2-YQkccImg_1MxgDRpV2IhWjYiV8QFYwexvtdTSdy9qeO0jnIFFu_L7pg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201118%2FLUAP3SKPE5D6HKBGAPT6CRVE7I%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2-YQkccImg_1MxgDRpV2IhWjYiV8QFYwexvtdTSdy9qeO0jnIFFu_L7pg&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5hTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=35887e67\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201118%2FLUAP3SKPE5D6HKBGAPT6CRVE7I%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dtwad_social_appledaily.tw%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2-YQkccImg_1MxgDRpV2IhWjYiV8QFYwexvtdTSdy9qeO0jnIFFu_L7pg&h=b84c2d27\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201118/LUAP3SKPE5D6HKBGAPT6CRVE7I/?utm_campaign=twad_social_appledaily.tw&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2-YQkccImg_1MxgDRpV2IhWjYiV8QFYwexvtdTSdy9qeO0jnIFFu_L7pg</a>"},{"pid":"1a44f965f91bb4c32c1e752dd64f043a1f64b3de","tid":2291112,"uid":123848,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"真係頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eadb2806d9645f705dd70df6c65239fc452ac171","tid":2291112,"uid":178205,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"1a44f965f91bb4c32c1e752dd64f043a1f64b3de","tid":2291112,"uid":123848,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"真係頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"這些機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hk